  <brief_title>A Study Comparing Radiofrequency Ablation and Hepatic Resection for Hepatocellular Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Study to Compare the Efficacy of Radiofrequency Ablation and Hepatic Resection as a Primary Treatment for Single Small Hepatocellular Carcinoma</official_title>
