  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective randomized study is to compare the efficacy and safety of
      radiofrequency ablation and hepatic resection for small hepatocellular carcinomas with very
      homogeneous underlying conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    The post-treatment recurrence rate was expected to be different between two treatment groups.
  </why_stopped>
